{
  "stem": "4078.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "However, when the Germans marched into Holland and-- or the rest of Europe and Holland fell, and most of-- and all of Europe fell-- the British government in their wisdom, I suppose, decided that they wanted to keep tabs on all aliens, friendly or otherwise.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans who lived in England and the Italians were rounded up and put into-- not concentration camps, but into sort of separate camps, somewhere or other.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I had a girlfriend in school whose father was from Italy, and he, like my father, never bothered to change his nationality.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her mother was English, and they took her father away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father they didn't take away, they just gave him and my mother, and, of course, me too, three days to move out of our house.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because where we lived in the suburbs of-- of London, we were near an airport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not really an airport, they called it an aerodrome, the North Hall Aerodrome, where the RAF were, were stationed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was not too far away from where we lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were afraid that my father might, in the middle of the night, get up and go walk over there and blow it up or whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were too close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Our house was too close to the, to the aerodrome.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they gave us three days to move closer to London.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was I think in 1940, we had to move.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We gave up our house, and-- and they gave us certain areas where we could live, in London proper.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we moved there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's what-- in the height of the Blitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were in the middle of the Blitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
